snippet.title: Ground of Aces - TactiCon 2024 - Alpha 2 Available Now - World War II Base Builder
snippet.description:
Play the exclusive TactiCon demo of GROUND OF ACES now: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2308690/Ground_of_Aces/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=youtubedescription

Check out TactiCon 2024:
https://store.steampowered.com/sale/Tacticon2024

GROUND OF ACES – The base building game that lets you take command of a remote air base of workers and pilots during World War II.

Enlist on our website:
https://www.groundofaces.com/
